        "note": "Original grammar structure and interpretations. Synthesized from the published research of Aaron Beck (CBT), Marsha Linehan (DBT), Sue Johnson (EFT), John Bowlby (attachment), Silvan Tomkins (affect theory), Paul Ekman (basic emotions), Jeffrey Young (schema therapy), Stephen Porges (polyvagal), Peter Fonagy (mentalization), Carl Rogers (person-centered), and Carl Jung (projection/shadow). No text copied from copyrighted works."
